Clone into ~/Library/Application Support/TextMate for single user install, or
/Library/Application Support/TextMate for system wide install. This requires the
Haskell.tmbundle.

I noticed that it currently isn't available on the TextMate Bundles SVN Trunk
anymore. So you should maybe search some revisions. Otherwise contact me.

This was the original post:
http://weblog.jamisbuck.org/2005/11/1/haskell-bundle-for-textmate